<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Red Dragonscale Armour Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Talk to Karam Dragonforge in the Rathe Mountains and he will give you the quest.<BR>
<BR>
2) Retrieve a red dragonscale from Lord Nagafen (This will be fun)<BR>
<BR>
3) Retrieve a vial of swirling smoke. (made by an enchanter)<BR>
<BR>
4) Take these 2 items and 1000pp to Karam to receive your Red Dragonscale Armour</div>
<BR>
